---
const testimonials = [
  {
    name: "Nicolas Gonzalez",
    role: "Android & Flutter Engineer at Globant",
    opinion:
      "Awesome working with you, continue being a hard worker, and keep updated in new technologies! I'm learning more from you inside the project along side with the teammates. Getting fully involved in a project, most of all going one step further by understanding how all the pieces live together in order to make certain feature work (iOS, Android and services). He is always open to help other members of the team or to provide assistance to new members. Keep rocking Raul!",
  },
  {
    name: "Juana De los Santos",
    role: "Flutter Developer Semi Senior at Globant | Advanced linguistics student",
    opinion:
      "There are not enough words to describe how much of a good leader and colleague you are. I think you have an great ability to guide the team, you know exactly how to create an environment where growth and collaboration thrive. You have shown it the last year and a half. As a developer, your expertise is unmatched. Your dedication, problem-solving skills, and willingness to support the team in any situation make you not only a remarkable professional but also a person anyone would be lucky to work with.",
  }
];
// Function to calculate `data-aos-duration` based on index
function calculateAosDuration(index) {
  return 1500 + index * 500; // Example: Increment duration by 500ms for each project
}
---

<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="px-8 2xl:max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <!-- Section Title and Decorative Elements -->
      <div
        class="h-0.5 bg-secondary"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
      >
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-secondary text-base font-medium"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="1500"
      >
        <span>human</span>
        <span class="font-bold">opinions</span>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col text-secondary pt-2 mt-2 gap-12 lg:gap-2">
      {
        testimonials.map((opinion, index) => (
          <div
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration={calculateAosDuration(index)}
            class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:items-end lg:grid-cols-4 py-4 gap-4"
          >
            <p class="text-xl  lg:col-span-3 lg:text-2xl  indent-24 lg:indent-24 text-right">
              {opinion.opinion}
            </p>
            <p class="italic text-xs block ">
              {opinion.name} {opinion.role}
            </p>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
